summary: Link test to the external issue tracker

story:
    As a user I want to track the connection between test and external system.

description:
    URL of an issue on the tracker which is relevant to the test.
    Should be a ``string`` or a ``list
    of strings``.

example: |
    issue: https://github.com/psss/tmt/issues/207
    issue:
      - https://github.com/psss/tmt/issues/207
      - https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1

implemented: /tmt/base
